### A 9-qubit Clifford+T circuit for the AES S-box. 
### Here, 9 qubits are labelled as number 0,1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8.
### NOT is a Pauli-X gate, TD is the inverse of T gate.
### CNOT(a,b) means a CNOT gate with the a-th qubit as the target qubit.

